To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Momentum _mom;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_mom = MOM(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_mom.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "momentum", _mom.Current.Value);
}
